      • Public Function ExportChanges(Optional comments As String = " ") As Long

        Public Function ExportChanges(Optional comments As String = " ") As Long
        Details:

        ' returns export tid
        ' 0 = no changes
        ' >0 = submit successful
        ' -1 = submit failed
        ' Critical Level Definition
        ' 1 = No automatic critical update unless explicitly specified
        ' 2 = Make critical update if columns are added
        ' 4 = Make critical update if columns are deleted
        ' 8 = Make critical update if rows are added
        ' 16 = Make critical update if rows are deleted
        ' 32 = Make critical update for any cell change
        ' Change Flag Definitions
        ' 1 = Value Change
        ' 2 = Formula Change
        ' 4 = Row Added
        ' 8 = Column Added
        ' 16 = Row Deleted
        ' 32 = Column Deleted
